{"tid":2313130,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"MMA 2020︱IZ*ONE是非不影響好成績　Oh My Girl出道5年首奪獎","createTime":"2020-12-05T13:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T23:44:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6d6c69f754518688a90f099a5ae5af2b2dda0ebe","tid":2313130,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"礙於新冠肺炎疫情影響，今年韓國頒獎典禮「Melon Music Awards 2020」（甜瓜音樂獎、簡稱MMA）改為線上舉行。除了BTS防彈少年團奪6獎成大贏家外，出道5年的Oh My Girl和因造馬事件是非不斷的IZ*ONE也首次獲大會頒發「TOP 10」。<br />\n<br />\n出道已5年的女團Oh My Girl今年憑一首《Nonstop》上位，苦等多年才獲邀參加頒獎禮，隊長效定講到：「這是Oh My Girl第一次參與MMA，很感謝第一次參與就給予我們大獎，在眾多歌手中被稱為『TOP 10』，覺得非常光榮及幸福。」效定坦言組合仍有很多不足，多謝粉絲多年來的支持及信任，表現出謙虛的一面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201205/412005612914741248931824.jpeg/wgoTdkHd_wHRbATyrCVOp2CEU5TpPySMUb_NgFG_zYA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201205%2F412005612914741248931824.jpeg%2FwgoTdkHd_wHRbATyrCVOp2CEU5TpPySMUb_NgFG_zYA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=59dcae19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一邊，IZ*ONE雖然最近再陷入選秀節目《Produce 48》造馬風波，但是非完全不影響她們的好成績，首次獲大會頒發「TOP 10」。IZ*ONE首先向粉絲道謝，感謝大家一直在身邊支持組合，承諾日後會以更帥氣的模樣報答大家。今晚IZ*ONE帶來了《FIESTA》和《Secret Story Of The Swan》外，她們將於明晚的「MAMA頒獎禮」上率先公開新歌《Panorama》，粉絲不能錯過。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201205/412005790837116928862534.jpeg/Nml7X3wu-XrQqGvD_SSUTkwDEKMaKor2mFS2EphUthI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201205%2F412005790837116928862534.jpeg%2FNml7X3wu-XrQqGvD_SSUTkwDEKMaKor2mFS2EphUthI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=298e0f8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dde0cb881dc7911f19641f020580b21b9b10f39","tid":2313130,"uid":256952,"like":7,"dislike":17,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T13:57:58.000Z","msg":"Oh My Girl快啲4<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4804f0c52d